		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The green windows on level 1 looks a little odd, but level 7 looks great.<br /><br />If you enjoy doing these, I say go for it with the rest of the games.<br /><br />Some of the games I've seen that are dark use a lot of black blended (dithered) with other colors. You might want to consider editing the graphics slightly, as well, to blend black in.<br /><br />Like Ninja Gaiden, level 5-1

		

